---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Case Studies | Zero Barriers"
  description="Zero Barriers Case Studies - Real-world examples of our breakthrough growth methodology delivering rapid, substantial, and sustainable results for businesses and individuals."
>
  <body>
    <Header />

    <!-- Case Studies Hero -->
    <section class="case-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h1>Client Success Stories</h1>
          <p>Transforming People and Businesses</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-img">
          <img src="/images/River.png" alt="Success visualization" />
        </div>
        <div class="section-title">
          <p>
            Our case studies demonstrate Zero Barriers' ability to engineer
            rapid, substantial, and sustainable growth through our systematic
            approach to transformation. By identifying barriers, adopting proven
            systems, adapting to individual strengths, and engineering success,
            we help both businesses and individuals achieve breakthrough
            results.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="contact.html" class="cta-button">Create Your Success Story</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SOS Support Case Study -->
    <section class="case-study-section">
      <div class="container case-study-container">
        <div class="case-study-image">
          <img
            src="/images/code.jpg"
            alt="SOS Support case study visualization"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="case-study-content">
          <span class="case-study-label">Business Transformation</span>
          <h2 class="case-study-title">
            SOS Support: Engineering Elite-Level Growth
          </h2>
          <div class="case-study-module">
            <h3 class="module-title">
              <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> The Gap: Barrier
            </h3>
            <p>
              As owner of SOS Support, Jason Kidman faced a critical challenge:
              how to build an elite firm without becoming its single point of
              failure. He needed to address multiple barriers including:
            </p>
            <ul class="barrier-list">
              <li>Location limitations</li>
              <li>Staffing capabilities</li>
              <li>Structural inefficiencies</li>
              <li>Capacity constraints</li>
              <li>Brand development needs</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="case-study-module">
            <h3 class="module-title">
              <i class="fas fa-bridge"></i> The Bridge: Solution
            </h3>
            <p>
              Zero Barriers implemented its comprehensive transformation
              approach:
            </p>
            <ul class="solution-list">
              <li>Served as Outsourced Sales and Service Manager</li>
              <li>
                Applied the four-phase Zero Barriers methodology:
                <ul class="solution-list" style="margin-top: 10px">
                  <li>Identified Barriers to Growth</li>
                  <li>Implemented System Adoption (Best Practices)</li>
                  <li>Facilitated System Adaptation (Own it)</li>
                  <li>Established KPI-driven Focus</li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>
                Provided comprehensive coaching and leadership development
              </li>
              <li>Aligned implementation with the owner's vision</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="case-link">
              <a href="services.html#methodology"
                >Learn more about our four-phase methodology
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="case-study-module">
            <h3 class="module-title">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> The Results: Success
            </h3>
            <div class="results-group">
              <div class="result-category">
                <h4 class="result-category-title">Rapid Growth:</h4>
                <ul class="results-list">
                  <li>122% growth in the first year</li>
                  <li>Expanded market share and reach</li>
                  <li>Enhanced team recruitment and retention</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="result-category">
                <h4 class="result-category-title">Substantial Growth:</h4>
                <ul class="results-list">
                  <li>Achieved back-to-back banner years (2016-2018)</li>
                  <li>Strengthened customer portfolio</li>
                  <li>Improved client retention and advocacy</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="result-category">
                <h4 class="result-category-title">Sustainable Growth:</h4>
                <ul class="results-list">
                  <li>Recognition as Utah One Hundred (2017, 2018)</li>
                  <li>Next Gen 250 Award (2017)</li>
                  <li>MSP 501 Global Award (2018)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <p class="testimonial-content">
              Shayne's coaching has benefited me personally and as an owner. The
              skills I've learned have been invaluable. I am a better
              businessman for engaging him... Shayne has helped me live a
              Purpose-Driven life.
            </p>
            <p class="testimonial-author">— Jason Kidman, Owner</p>
          </div>
          <div class="case-link">
            <a href="services.html#partnerships"
              >See how our partnerships enhanced this solution
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Michelle Atkinson Case Study -->
    <section class="case-study-section">
      <div class="container case-study-container">
        <div class="case-study-image">
          <img
            src="/images/typing.jpg"
            alt="Michelle Atkinson case study visualization"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="case-study-content">
          <span class="case-study-label">Personal Transformation</span>
          <h2 class="case-study-title">
            Personal Transformation: L. Michelle Atkinson
          </h2>
          <div class="case-study-module">
            <h3 class="module-title">
              <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> The Gap: Barrier
            </h3>
            <p>
              As VP of Operations & Finance at SOS Support, Michelle struggled
              with:
            </p>
            <ul class="barrier-list">
              <li>Professional fulfillment despite success</li>
              <li>Recurring burnout cycles</li>
              <li>Misalignment between skills and passion</li>
              <li>Career transitions every three years</li>
              <li>Impact on personal well-being</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="case-study-module">
            <h3 class="module-title">
              <i class="fas fa-bridge"></i> The Bridge: Solution
            </h3>
            <p>
              Zero Barriers implemented its Purpose-Driven transformation
              approach:
            </p>
            <ul class="solution-list">
              <li>Comprehensive Purpose Exercise implementation</li>
              <li>Regular coaching sessions</li>
              <li>Five-step process execution</li>
              <li>Focus on authentic decision-making</li>
              <li>Barrier removal strategies</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="case-link">
              <a href="services.html#human"
                >Learn more about our Purpose-Driven Exercise
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="case-study-module">
            <h3 class="module-title">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> The Results: Success
            </h3>
            <div class="results-group">
              <div class="result-category">
                <h4 class="result-category-title">Rapid Growth:</h4>
                <ul class="results-list">
                  <li>Immediate attitude and focus transformation</li>
                  <li>Enhanced decision-making confidence</li>
                  <li>Career advancement and promotion</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="result-category">
                <h4 class="result-category-title">Substantial Growth:</h4>
                <ul class="results-list">
                  <li>Improved work-life integration</li>
                  <li>Strengthened professional relationships</li>
                  <li>Increased personal fulfillment</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="result-category">
                <h4 class="result-category-title">Sustainable Growth:</h4>
                <ul class="results-list">
                  <li>Sustained positive mindset transformation</li>
                  <li>Enhanced self-talk and confidence</li>
                  <li>Improved relationship dynamics</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <p class="testimonial-content">
              Being purpose-oriented has given me direction, freedom,
              fulfillment, confidence, peace, success, happiness, and love, in
              multiple arenas of my life. It set me free and lit me on fire!
            </p>
            <p class="testimonial-author">— L. Michelle Atkinson</p>
          </div>
          <div class="case-link">
            <a href="services.html#purpose"
              >Discover the values that drive our transformation approach
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Darrell Rawlins Case Study -->
    <section class="case-study-section">
      <div class="container case-study-container">
        <div class="case-study-image">
          <img
            src="/images/teamwork.jpg"
            alt="Darrell Rawlins case study visualization"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="case-study-content">
          <span class="case-study-label">Sales Transformation</span>
          <h2 class="case-study-title">
            B2C to B2B Transformation: Darrell Rawlins
          </h2>
          <div class="case-study-module">
            <h3 class="module-title">
              <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> The Gap: Barrier
            </h3>
            <p>
              As a Client Advisor in Benefits & HR Consulting, Darrell faced:
            </p>
            <ul class="barrier-list">
              <li>Transition challenges from B2C to B2B sales</li>
              <li>Extended sales cycle adaptation</li>
              <li>Confidence and ability doubts</li>
              <li>Need for sustainable income stability</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="case-study-module">
            <h3 class="module-title">
              <i class="fas fa-bridge"></i> The Bridge: Solution
            </h3>
            <p>Zero Barriers deployed its comprehensive toolkit:</p>
            <ul class="solution-list">
              <li>IMPROV Sales System implementation</li>
              <li>Purpose-Driven Exercise integration</li>
              <li>The Attitude Cycle methodology</li>
              <li>Individual and team coaching</li>
              <li>Personalized strength adaptation</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="case-link">
              <a href="services.html#revenue"
                >Learn more about our IMPROV Sales Methodology
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="case-study-module">
            <h3 class="module-title">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> The Results: Success
            </h3>
            <div class="results-group">
              <div class="result-category">
                <h4 class="result-category-title">Rapid Growth:</h4>
                <ul class="results-list">
                  <li>Record-setting appointment generation</li>
                  <li>Created "Mutual Discovery Tsunamis"</li>
                  <li>Outperformed industry veterans</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="result-category">
                <h4 class="result-category-title">Substantial Growth:</h4>
                <ul class="results-list">
                  <li>Successfully bridged B2C to B2B gap</li>
                  <li>Developed consultative selling expertise</li>
                  <li>Enhanced client relationship capabilities</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="result-category">
                <h4 class="result-category-title">Sustainable Growth:</h4>
                <ul class="results-list">
                  <li>Established authentic purpose alignment</li>
                  <li>Increased client investment and trust</li>
                  <li>Sustained high-performance results</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <p class="testimonial-content">
              Shayne helped me find a purpose in my field and having that
              purpose creates an authenticity that my prospects and clients feel
              and resonate with. I don't feel fake when I offer my services to
              potential customers; I feel more invested in the success of my
              clients' goals.
            </p>
            <p class="testimonial-author">— Darrell Rawlins</p>
          </div>
          <div class="case-link">
            <a href="services.html#technology"
              >See how our CRM partnerships enhance sales transformation
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container cta-content">
        <h2>Create Your Success Story</h2>
        <p>Ready to transform your business or career with Zero Barriers?</p>
        <a href="contact.html" class="white-cta"
          >Schedule Your Transformation Assessment</a
        >
        <div>
          <a href="services.html#methodology" class="secondary-white-cta"
            >Explore Our Methodology <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</Layout>
